#+title: Doing Philosophy

* Introduction
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       ba428283-5d92-4c63-804c-1d5c77c9c253
:END:
- The _ancient Greeks_ used the term [[id:96c66d5d-1489-43e1-b3c6-a9d5d1427e2f][Philosophy]] to refer to "*Love of wisdom*".
- [[id:96c66d5d-1489-43e1-b3c6-a9d5d1427e2f][Philosophy]] came from two words:
  + "/philos/" which means *love*
  + "/sophia/" which means *wisdom*
* [[id:96c66d5d-1489-43e1-b3c6-a9d5d1427e2f][Philosophy]]
